Commentary Text: Mustafizur to Arshdeep Singh, out Arshdeep Singh Run Out!! Sums up PBKS innings this run-out. Comical stuff. Yorker length outside off, Arshdeep Singh swings and misses, he runs and sees Vaibhav Arora not responding. Pant jogs and whips the bails off. Bewildered look on Arshdeep's face. Vaibhav never was interested in a single and PBKS have been bowled out for 115. Arshdeep Singh run out (Pant) 9(17) [4s-2]
